trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of interfaces for use in Web Parts connections.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma coleção de interfaces para uso em conexões de Web Parts.

trans-unit.source: Communication between a provider and consumer requires a contract defined in an interface.
trans-unit.target: Comunicação entre um provedor e consumidor exige um contrato definido em uma interface.

trans-unit.source: This collection contains all the communication interfaces supported by the consumer.
trans-unit.target: Esta coleção contém todas as interfaces de comunicação com suporte pelo consumidor.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProviderConnectionPoint.GetSecondaryInterfaces%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method returns a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: O método <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProviderConnectionPoint.GetSecondaryInterfaces%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> retorna um objeto <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection>.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: A collection of objects to convert into a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Uma coleção de objetos a ser convertida em um <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" /> class with the specified collection.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" /> com a coleção especificada.

trans-unit.source: An object in <paramref name="connectionInterfaces" /> cannot be added to a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" /> collection.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto no <paramref name="connectionInterfaces" /> não pode ser adicionado a uma coleção <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" /> to combine with the <c>connectionInterfaces</c> object.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" /> a ser combinado com o objeto <c>connectionInterfaces</c>.

trans-unit.source: A collection to combine with the <c>existingConnectionInterfaces</c> object.
trans-unit.target: Uma coleção a ser combinada com o objeto <c>existingConnectionInterfaces</c>.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" /> class by combining the two specified collections.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" /> combinando as duas coleções especificadas.

trans-unit.source: An object in <paramref name="connectionInterfaces" /> cannot be added to a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" /> collection.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto no <paramref name="connectionInterfaces" /> não pode ser adicionado a uma coleção <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The type to locate in the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: O tipo a ser localizado no <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" /> object contains a specific value.
trans-unit.target: Determina se um objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" /> contém um valor específico.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <paramref name="value" /> is found in the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se <paramref name="value" /> for encontrado no <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" />; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Array" /> that is the destination of the elements copied from <see cref="T:System.Collections.ReadOnlyCollectionBase" />.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Array" /> unidimensional que é o destino dos elementos copiados de <see cref="T:System.Collections.ReadOnlyCollectionBase" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Array" /> must have zero-based indexing.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Array" /> deve ter indexação com base em zero.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in <c>array</c> at which copying begins.
trans-unit.target: O índice baseado em zero na <c>array</c> na qual a cópia começa.

trans-unit.source: Copies the entire <see cref="T:System.Collections.ReadOnlyCollectionBase" /> object to a compatible one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Array" />, starting at the specified index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: Copia todo o objeto <see cref="T:System.Collections.ReadOnlyCollectionBase" /> para um <see cref="T:System.Array" /> unidimensional compatível, começando no índice especificado da matriz de destino.

trans-unit.source: References a static, read-only instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Referencia uma instância estática e somente leitura da classe <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The type to locate in the collection.
trans-unit.target: O tipo a ser localizado na coleção.

trans-unit.source: Searches for the specified object and returns the zero-based index of the first occurrence within the entire <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" /> collection.
trans-unit.target: Pesquisa o objeto especificado e retorna o índice de base zero da primeira ocorrência dentro de toda a coleção <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the first occurrence of <paramref name="value" /> within the entire <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" />, if found; otherwise, -1.
trans-unit.target: O índice baseado em zero da primeira ocorrência de <paramref name="value" /> em todo o <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" />, se encontrado; caso contrário, -1.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the element to get.
trans-unit.target: O índice baseado em zero do elemento a ser obtido.

trans-unit.source: Gets the element at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o elemento no índice especificado.

trans-unit.source: The element at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: O elemento no índice especificado.
